Maintainer: Xiao Jing Guo <xiaojing.guo@nrcan-rncan.gc.ca>
Description: CFSTRenD streamlines the processing and analysis of tree-ring data. Key features include manipulation and summarization of tree-ring data, data quality identification and classification, flexible detrending and climate-growth modeling using generalized additive mixed models (GAMM), and visual inspection of data summaries, quality, and model performance. This provides a comprehensive toolkit for the CFS-TRenD community and dendrochronologists.
